    description:
      "A fresh and healthy salad with tomatoes, cucumbers, olives, and feta.",
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    title: "Bruschetta",
    price: 7.99,
    image: "Bruschetta.jpg",
    description:
      "Grilled bread topped with a mixture of diced tomatoes, garlic, and basil.",
